summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of that portion of Lot 21, Block 5, Cedar Park Addition lying between a line 150' easterly of and parallel to the east boundary of Bothell Way and a line 60' easterly of and parallel to the aforementioned line; with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-366 and 17-279, respectively.
